		<h1 class="title">
							VirtueMart 2.0.14, Seminar, and books					</h1>
	
				<p class="meta">
	
			Written by Valérie Isaksen on <time datetime="2012-11-13" pubdate>13 November 2012</time>. 	
		
		</p>
		
	</header>
		
	
	<div class="content clearfix">

		
