		<h1 class="title">
							End of life for VirtueMart 1.1, Heidelpay now in VirtueMart 2.0.12					</h1>
	
				<p class="meta">
	
			Written by Valérie Isaksen on <time datetime="2012-10-04" pubdate>04 October 2012</time>. 	
		
		</p>
		
	</header>
		
	
	<div class="content clearfix">

		
		<script language="Javascript">

